{
  "name": "DiscussNav-MP3D",
  "description": "DiscussNav (Long et al., 2024) multi-LLM discussion VLN port for R2R / MP3D. Uses 12-direction panorama scan, RAM tags + InstructBLIP captions, completion-estimation LLM, pred_vp with n=5 sampling, thought-fusion + decision-testing experts, then env step. step_budget=7 mirrors paper hyperparameter. [LLM profile switched 2026-05-10 from openai-gpt4 \u2192 openai (gpt-4o) for ~10x cost cut + automatic prompt caching on stable system_prompt prefixes; revert if multi-expert quality regresses.]",
